reviewText: As good as I remembered it from it's showing at the Minneapolis Underground Film Festival! An indy laugh-riot!

I am not much on movies but when I saw this one I knew it was different; boy was I right!! This is not your standard movie!! This is a well thought out, well played out, gut buster!!!! If you do not have this one in your collection order it NOW!!!!
Fast paced with endless quick verbal jibes, Dynamite Swine is a must for anyone who wants a rowdy time.  See it with a throng of buddies and babes - you'll all have a hoot!
